One of the best protections for those with type 2 diabetes is to keep the disease under control through exercise, a healthy diet and the help of healthcare professionals.
The coronary heart disease epidemic, however, has made it difficult for many to maintain a routine.
The high price of insulin has forced some to keep coming to work and risk being exposed to the virus.
